近，應該都要六七分鐘），有河畔花園嘅食肆，行一段仔路可以去沙田市中心、第一城（都要行三個字）<br />\n我自己就覺得環境幾靜，價錢又抵<br />\n不過就聽聞個度唔知係多蟲定係多老鼠，但住得舊樓附近有餐廳都預咗<br />\n<br />\n大個住九龍，但老實講句，去土瓜灣次數少之又少，我知道個度雖然無黨鐵，但交通好方便，不過我次次都係土瓜灣塞車，所以真係唔太會考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bceae529c2bdcfd9df7938744459e932118486ef","tid":2450882,"uid":324964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:28:17.000Z","msg":"新城中心 花園城 一個土瓜灣一個沙田 點解巴打拎佢哋兩個比?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83221fe16d1130b43f39c3618907c291cdf2ce4a","tid":2450882,"uid":26071,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T18:26:58.000Z","msg":"生活圈/返工去開邊頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n500萬300呎嘅細價樓好多地區都有<br />\n最緊要自己方便嘅啫<br />\n<br />\n如果aim兩三年後換樓就最好大路少少嘅<br />\neg 德寶/河畔/大埔中心/屯門市廣場"},{"pid":"49a762bee67df6412d2a1abd145c9948d97fe135","tid":2450882,"uid":227275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T18:29:19.000Z","msg":"是旦市區居屋"},{"pid":"9b85199e1c45bc36fe19063a056bc8a54aba3ea0","tid":2450882,"uid":82262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83221fe16d1130b43f39c3618907c291cdf2ce4a","tid":2450882,"uid":26071,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T18:26:58.000Z","msg":"生活圈/返工去開邊頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n500萬300呎嘅細價樓好多地區都有<br />\n最緊要自己方便嘅啫<br />\n<br />\n如果aim兩三年後換樓就最好大路少少嘅<br />\neg 德寶/河畔/大埔中心/屯門市廣場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T00:24:13.000Z","msg":"德寶不了<br />\n揀樂雅苑唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6511b99b33ec962664714fb2481ca0695583cb9","tid":2450882,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bceae529c2bdcfd9df7938744459e932118486ef","tid":2450882,"uid":324964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB